{
  "stem": "8786.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But these people were not dead yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were just in middle of dying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was the first night of-- first night of our march.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The second march-- the second night, I remember that we were just begging each other, this is-- this is a lost game.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This is a-- this is the last trip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Last-- The next night, we came through a town Loretto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I don't know whether-- how to explain it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But this was a very customary thing among this-- every little village, every little town or city, before the last German army group went through it or trucks, they made barricades into the width of the-- of the street.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Make believe that this is a street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This is-- this is the width of a street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put in barricades.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the barricade was they putting in long pieces of poles-- how do you call?-- beams-- beams.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they left open only so much that a truck should go through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the very last group before the-- the last truck will go through, they will fill that in too, in order that it should be-- the highway should be totally blocked, that the Russians shouldn't be able to go through it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know whether the Russian-- I don't think the Russian tanks were afraid of this, because they could probably go up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this was in every town you could see this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made a ditch and they filled it in on the left side and on the-- beams, long beams.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And leave open just as much that the marchers and the trucks should go through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this Loretto was like this, except that the Germans, what they did, the local people wanted to have fun.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
